Business Summary


Designs, manufactures and distributes LCD (liquid crystal display) screensCPT Technology (Group) Co., Ltd. engages in the research and development, design, production, sales, and after-sales service of flat panel display devices, liquid crystal displays, modules, and components.It specializes in liquid crystal module, cover glass, and panel products.The company was founded in December 1992 and is headquartered in Fuzhou, China.Number of employees : 5 882 persons.
 





