Description




CPT TECHNOLOGY (GROUP) CO.,LTD is a China-based company principally engaged in the processing and distribution of liquid crystal display (LCD) modules. The Company’s main products include large-size Thin Film Transistor Liquid Crystal Displays (TFT-LCDs), medium- and small-size TFT-LCDs, cover lens, flat display components and products, LCD monitors, backlight modules and spare parts, among others. The Company's products are applied in LCD televisions, laptops, monitors, computer monitors, smart phones, tablet computers and vehicle displays, among others. The Company mainly distributes its products in domestic market and to overseas markets.


More from Reuters »








