Summary for Cpt Technology (Group) Co.,Ltd.
CPT TECHNOLOGY (GROUP) CO., LTD. is principally engaged in the research, development, design, manufacture and distribution of electronic products. The Company operates its businesses primarily through the manufacture and processing of liquid crystal display (LCD) modules. The Company primarily provides flat display components and products, LCD monitors, modules and spare parts, among others. The Company mainly distributes its products in domestic markets and to overseas markets.


