Company Description                    




                        CPT Technology Group Company Limited is principally engaged in flat panel display, LCD, display modules and components development , design , production, sales and after-sales service . CPT Technology, formerly known as Mindong Electric ( Group) Company Limited and in 2011 was changed into CPT Technology (Group ) Co., Ltd. The company was established in 1993 and is headquartered in Fuzhou, Fujian Province.                     


